Definition at line 41 of file CMSLOCResult.php.

$logicalLines = 0

Logical lines of code.

Logical lines are determined by:

Each semi-colon represents 1 point. Each block declaration (such as a class, function, etc declaration) represents 1 point. Each statement (if, while etc) represents 1 point. 'for' statements represent 3 points.
